      "representative_excerpt": "I strongly oppose allowing bear baiting on lands managed by the National Park Service. Bear baiting involves placing piles of human food in the environment to lure bears to predictable locations where they can be easily killed. This practice artificially manipulates wildlife behavior and encourages bears to associate human activity with food. It\u2019s dangerous ...",
