      "representative_excerpt": "I would like to express my opposition to bear-baiting, especially in National Parks. These parks are the few places nature has left to thrive. Humans are forcing many species into extinction. It is time for us to care more about our planet and environment, particularly with ensuring that our wildlife has places to thrive. Thank you.",
